These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: iris, amaryllis, daisy, zinnia
There 4 different types of food: radish, eggplant, tomato, strawberry
1. the person who growsiris is on the right of the person eating tomato##1
2. the person eating strawberry is on the far left##1
3. the person eating tomato is between the person eating eggplant and the person who growsamaryllis##2
4. the person who growszinnia is on the far left##1
5. the person who growsdaisy is between the person who growsamaryllis and the person who growsiris##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Flower   | zinnia         | amaryllis   | daisy | iris       |
| Food      | strawberry | radish | tomato   | eggplant |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
4 different games are played: whist, canasta, poker, snooker
City: hamburg, venice, paris, new-york
1. the person traveling to new-york is between the person playing poker and the person traveling to venice##2
2. the person playing snooker is on the far right##1
3. the person traveling to paris is on the right of the person traveling to hamburg##1
4. the person playing whist is on the left of the person traveling to hamburg##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Game         | canasta | whist | poker | snooker |
| City   | venice    | new-york   | hamburg | paris       |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-3::.
The people grow 4 different varities of flowers: tulip, lily, orchid, daisy
4 different games are played: go, bridge, snooker, domino
1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
2. the person playing snooker is between the person playing bridge and the person who growslily##2
3. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
4. the person playing domino is on the left of the person who growsorchid##1
5. the person who growslily is the person playing domino##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |      2      |   3    |     4      |
| Flower          | daisy    | tulip | lily   | orchid  |
| Game   | bridge | snooker   | domino | go |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-4::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  coach, doctor, firefighter, mechanic
The people use 4 different means of transport: quad-bike, motorbike, subway, van
1. the person driving the motorbike is the doctor##1
2. the coach is between the person driving the quad-bike and the mechanic##2
3. the person driving the motorbike is on the far right##1
4. the coach is on the right of the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1   |   2    |     3      |    4     |
| Job     | mechanic   | coach    | firefighter       | doctor   |
| Transport   | subway | van | quad-bike | motorbike |

 #################################

 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-5::.
There are 4 different nationalities: dutch, french, chinese, australian
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: bluemaster, havana, ritmeester, cain
1. the dutch is on the left of the chinese##1
2. the ritmeester-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the bluemaster-smoker is on the far right##1
4. the australian is between the bluemaster-smoker and the havana-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |      1       |    2     |     3     |       4       |
| Nationality   | dutch        | chinese | australian  | french |
| Cigar      | ritmeester | havana  | cain | bluemaster    |

