.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-6::.
4 different pets are kept: rat, ferret, bird, lizard
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, september, february, december
1. the person who's birthday is in february is on the right of the person who's birthday is in september##1
2. the owner of the lizard is the person who's birthday is in february##1
3. the owner of the lizard is on the far right##1
4. the owner of the ferret is the person who's birthday is in august##1
5. the owner of the bird is between the owner of the rat and the owner of the ferret##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |       2       |     3     |   4    |
| Pet   | ferret     | bird           | rat | lizard  |
| Birthday         | august | december | september   | february |

