.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-7::.
The people prefer 4 different types of sport: water-polo, swimming, rowing, handball
The people have 4 different jobs:  software-developer, chef, engineer, designer
1. the person who's sport is swimming is the software-developer##1
2. the engineer is on the left of the software-developer##1
3. the designer is on the right of the person who's sport is water-polo##1
4. the chef is on the left of the designer##1
5. the person who's sport is water-polo is between the software-developer and the person who's sport is rowing##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |   1    |   2    |     3      |     4      |
| Sport   | handball   | swimming | water-polo | rowing      |
| Job     | engineer | software-developer    | chef  | designer |

