.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-8::.
There are 4 different favourite beverages: iced-tea, tea, lemonade, 7up
The people have 4 different jobs:  fisherman, project-manager, software-developer, teacher
1. the fisherman is the person drinking tea##1
2. the project-manager is between the person drinking lemonade and the software-developer##2
3. the person drinking iced-tea is on the far left##1
4. the fisherman is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1     |       2       |     3      |     4      |
| Beverage       | iced-tea | 7up | lemonade     | tea   |
| Job   | software-developer   | project-manager     | teacher | fisherman |

