.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-9::.
4 different pets are kept: fish, horse, guinea-pig, hamster
There are 4 different nationalities: brazilian, russian, spanish, pakistani
1. the owner of the guinea-pig is between the brazilian and the owner of the fish##2
2. the pakistani is on the left of the owner of the fish##1
3. the owner of the hamster is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
4. the brazilian is on the left of the pakistani##1
5. the owner of the fish is on the left of the spanish##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |      1       |     2     |     3      |      4       |
| Pet         | horse | guinea-pig | fish | hamster |
| Nationality   | brazilian         | pakistani       | russian    | spanish         |

