.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-10::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: may, august, june, april
There are 4 different nationalities: thai, indonesian, nigerian, canadian
1. the indonesian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
2. the nigerian is on the right of the person who's birthday is in june##1
3. the person who's birthday is in may is on the right of the person who's birthday is in august##1
4. the nigerian is on the right of the indonesian##1
5. the indonesian is between the person who's birthday is in august and the canadian##2

.:: Answer ::.
|         |   1    |     2      |    3     |    4     |
| Birthday    | april   | june      | august   | may  |
| Nationality   | canadian | indonesian | nigerian | thai |

