.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-11::.
The people have 4 different jobs:  manager, fisherman, security-guard, chef
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: punk, indie, soul, pop
1. the fan pop is on the right of the fan indie##1
2. the fisherman is between the chef and the manager##2
3. the fan indie is on the right of the fan soul##1
4. the fan soul is on the right of the manager##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1     |      2      |    3    |      4      |
| Job          | manager     | fisherman | chef   | security-guard        |
| Music-Genre   | punk | soul   | indie | pop |

