.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-12::.
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: pall-mall, bluemaster, alhambra, game
4 different pets are kept: lizard, goldfish, snake, dog
1. the owner of the snake is the bluemaster-smoker##1
2. the owner of the goldfish is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
3. the owner of the lizard is the pall-mall-smoker##1
4. the alhambra-smoker is the owner of the goldfish##1
5. the owner of the lizard is on the right of the game-smoker##1
6. the owner of the goldfish is between the bluemaster-smoker and the game-smoker##2

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2    |    3    |     4      |
| Cigar         | bluemaster | alhambra | game | pall-mall |
| Pet   | snake          | goldfish     | dog  | lizard     |

