.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-17::.
City: berlin, paris, liverpool, hamburg
The people have 4 different hobbies: chess, cooking, reading, video-games
1. the person traveling to berlin is on the right of the person who's hobby is video-games##1
2. the person traveling to hamburg is the person who's hobby is reading##1
3. the person who's hobby is cooking is between the person who's hobby is chess and the person traveling to paris##2
4. the person who's hobby is video-games is the person who's hobby is video-games##1
5. the person who's hobby is video-games is on the right of the person who's hobby is reading##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1    |    2    |    3     |     4     |
| City   | hamburg | paris | berlin | liverpool |
| Hobby           | reading  | video-games  | cooking | chess      |

