.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-18::.
City: boston, san-francisco, marseilles, edinburgh
4 different brands of cigars are smoked: alhambra, cain, vegafina, baccarat
1. the cain-smoker is on the right of the alhambra-smoker##1
2. the alhambra-smoker is on the far left##1
3. the person traveling to san-francisco is between the alhambra-smoker and the person traveling to marseilles##2
4. the person traveling to edinburgh is the alhambra-smoker##1
5. the person traveling to boston is on the right of the baccarat-smoker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|             |    1    |    2    |       3       |     4      |
| City       | edinburgh | san-francisco | marseilles | boston |
| Cigar   | alhambra    | cain  | baccarat    | vegafina       |

