.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-19::.
The people's birthday is in 4 different months: august, october, december, july
The people perfer 4 different movie-genres: zombie, martial-arts, disaster, epic
1. the person watching martial-arts movies is on the left of the person watching epic movies##1
2. the person watching zombie movies is on the left of the person watching martial-arts movies##1
3. the person who's birthday is in july is the person watching zombie movies##1
4. the person watching epic movies is between the person who's birthday is in august and the person who's birthday is in december##2
5. the person who's birthday is in december is the person watching disaster movies##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Birthday   | july   | august   | october | december |
| Movie-Genre         | zombie | martial-arts | epic     | disaster    |

