.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-20::.
The people prefer 4 different music-genres: reggae, trance, funk, country
4 different games are played: snooker, bridge, backgammon, whist
1. the person playing bridge is on the far left##1
2. the fan reggae is between the person playing snooker and the fan country##2
3. the fan country is on the left of the fan reggae##1
4. the fan trance is on the far right##1
5. the fan trance is on the right of the person playing backgammon##1

.:: Answer ::.
|         |     1      |     2      |     3      |    4    |
| Music-Genre   | funk    | country     | reggae | trance |
| Game     | bridge | whist | backgammon       | snooker     |

 